{"tid":2435533,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知道加左稅之後 炒窩輪牛熊有咩影響","createTime":"2021-03-06T10:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T06:29:46.000Z","uid":162540,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4693652c5654d9723de3a67c5094aeded4cc6313","tid":2435533,"uid":162540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"本身做開幾隻大股嘅牛熊多 爬下格仔。<br />\n<br />\n而家啲牛熊spread(買賣差價）多數係兩個價位平手 加咗稅之後 d大行（發行商）唔知會否在加大個spread 如果係 賺一兩格呢種玩法會gg。<br />\n<br />\n以我所知 大行會為d衍生產品做對沖 不過係唔知對沖到咩程度 涉及買賣正股就會要交稅 依家要加多左稅 自自然然成本就會轉嫁落產品到。<br />\n<br />\n不過又咁 舉個例子 平時騰訊一部分牛熊證 如果計返個槓桿 同買正股比較 你會發覺大行開出黎個spread根本唔足以彌補返要交既稅項。由此我有幾樣嘢覺得。<br />\n<br />\n首先，佢哋根本冇乜做對沖 如果唔係 交稅都交死佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n其次，買牛熊好過買正股 如果大行又冇縮vol 同睇啱方向的話。<br />\n<br />\n又， 好似聽一啲朋友講過 大行做對沖好似可以豁免咗交稅 呢點想要確認一下。<br />\n<br />\n入左行冇耐 都幾擔心加稅嘅情況出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用機炒賺少少係咪已經唔使玩 咁可以早啲謀定後路。有ching知道既話 希望講多兩句 感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34de2ac5ecab61633e5a2e9684b40733fcfc0ebf","tid":2435533,"uid":24570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:03:19.000Z","msg":"幾時開始加？"},{"pid":"134df33f0c93bb5cfea6c2e5ae766faf3f66e37b","tid":2435533,"uid":162540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34de2ac5ecab61633e5a2e9684b40733fcfc0ebf","tid":2435533,"uid":24570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:03:19.000Z","msg":"幾時開始加？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:05:10.000Z","msg":"未過立法會 預定8月1號開始。"},{"pid":"a1d9ec451691d5876d9033a7f78e8469cc2860d4","tid":2435533,"uid":162540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:11:53.000Z","msg":"有個藍屍話（唔理政治立場 以金融角度黎講算係okay）<br />\n加稅根本就係大陸所期待<br />\n主要係減少大陸資金炒港股嘅熱情程度 防止走資。<br />\n所以加嘅可能性都幾高<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/share/258189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2Fshare%2F258189&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1nxyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=127e9fd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/share/258189</a>"},{"pid":"82b4002ada7c41bf720eb3f39a3e736c94d70d41","tid":2435533,"uid":5278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:07:49.000Z","msg":"師兄<br />\n窩輪牛熊好似不嬲唔洗交stamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922f774f5fbf875c74a13efe74d1193b9fd82a55","tid":2435533,"uid":162540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82b4002ada7c41bf720eb3f39a3e736c94d70d41","tid":2435533,"uid":5278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:07:49.000Z","msg":"師兄<br />\n窩輪牛熊好似不嬲唔洗交stamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:38:16.000Z","msg":"發行商 要做對沖 嗰陣時買正股正路要交稅。<br />\n窩輪牛熊可能就係因為咁避免咗雙重課稅。"},{"pid":"c2488580172fdbb74df31bf92b418045fc86b5cb","tid":2435533,"uid":162540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:29:46.000Z","msg":"push"}]}